**2022: Argentina** - At the time of their victory in the 2022 FIFA World Cup, the President of Argentina was Alberto Ángel Fernández.

**2018: France** - Emmanuel Macron was the President of France when France won the 2018 FIFA World Cup.

**2014: Germany** - The Chancellor of Germany at the time of their win, Angela Merkel, was the head of the German government.

**2010: Spain** - Spain's head of government during their FIFA World Cup win was Prime Minister José Luis Rodríguez Zapatero.

**2006: Italy** - Romano Prodi was the President of the Council of Ministers (Prime Minister) of Italy when they won the 2006 FIFA World Cup.
